          "type": "text",
          "text": "Scheduler.DistributionReport",
          "marks": [
            {
              "type": "code"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": " table. It modifies various attributes of a distribution report, such as its name, description, associated job, and output format. Additionally, it updates parameter mappings for the report using another stored procedure, "
